   <name>Small Craft Advisory issued September 13 at 12:57PM EDT until September 14 at 11:00PM EDT by NWS Jacksonville FL</name>
   <styleUrl>#sev_minor</styleUrl>
   <Style>
    <BalloonStyle />
   </Style>
   <Snippet>* WHAT...Northeast winds 15 to 25 kt with occasional gusts up to
35 kt and seas 6 to 9 ft.

* WHERE...All Southeast Georgia and Northeast Florida coastal
waters from Altamaha Sound GA to Flagler Beach FL out to 60 NM.

* WHEN...Until 11 PM EDT Sunday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.</Snippet>
